::Fliq::

Fliq stops atop a small hill, looking at the scene below him. Its been 
a while since he&#39;d seen such a wreckage, probably not since his ship 
had crashed on the moon. He cautiously approaches, looking around the 
wreck, and the one good shuttle, to see if there was anyone 
functional. His hand remained close to his gun.




