&gt; --- In nbwrpg@y..., Kevin Ramsey &lt;kramsey20@y...&gt; wrote:
&gt; &gt; He thought he&#39;d evaded them, then as he passed Mars,
&gt; &gt; the Decepticon shuttle came out from behind Phobos.
&gt; &gt; Inside, Scud and Razor fired gleefully at the fleeing
&gt; &gt; shuttle. The shuttle itself was being fired on...and
&gt; &gt; boy was it taking damage. 
&gt; &gt; 
&gt; &gt; The odd thing was...it also had the Decepticon emblem.
&gt; &gt; Then a large explosion.
&gt; &gt; 
&gt; &gt; The Stabilizers were hit....and it was going down. The
&gt; &gt; pilot of the fleeing Decepticon shuttle guided it into
&gt; &gt; the atmosphere, hoping to at least survive a crash
&gt; &gt; landing long enough to make a last stand.
&gt; &gt; 
&gt; &gt; It was beginning to burn up in the atmosphere, headed
&gt; &gt; for land...Central Africa.
&gt; &gt; 
&gt; &gt; The plummet took forever. To the naked eye, the
&gt; &gt; crashing shuttle appeared as a comet, falling to Earth
&gt; &gt; in a burning fireball...
&gt; &gt; 
&gt; &gt; until it crashed hard in Central Africa. It skidded
&gt; &gt; nearly a mile before crashing to a stop. It was a
&gt; &gt; miracle that the craft was still relatively in one
&gt; &gt; piece...albiet shredded to ribbons.
&gt; &gt; 
&gt; &gt; Two minutes later, the other Decepticon shuttle
&gt; &gt; landed. Out came Scud (black) and Razor (dark red),
&gt; &gt; two Jet-class Decepticons disembarked, ready to finish
&gt; &gt; the job.
&gt; &gt; 
&gt; &gt; They blasted open the cockpit, to find no one there.
&gt; &gt; 
&gt; &gt; &quot;Oh Strafe...STRA-AFE! Come out come out wherever you
&gt; &gt; are!&quot; Scud shouted in an echoing, insane voice.
&gt; &gt; 
&gt; &gt; Razor was looking around, scanning the immediate area.
&gt; &gt; 
&gt; &gt; Razor laughed, &quot;Come on, you traitor. Come out so we
&gt; &gt; can take your head back to Cybertron!&quot;
&gt; &gt; 
&gt; &gt; Nothing.
&gt; &gt; 
&gt; &gt; Then a sound from the sky...
&gt; &gt; 
&gt; &gt; What appeared to be a dark blue F-22 Raptor did a full
&gt; &gt; Stuka dive bombing run, blasting away with twin laser
&gt; &gt; blasters mounted under the wings. The strafing run
&gt; &gt; took Razor from behind. Scud never had a chance.
&gt; &gt; 
&gt; &gt; ...and fell, blasted like crazy.
&gt; &gt; 
&gt; &gt; Razor, however was able to dodge the strafing run. As
&gt; &gt; the jet passed by, it transformed into a robot and
&gt; &gt; landed, the twin blasters forming a double-barreled
&gt; &gt; laser cannon. He was sleek, streamlined 
&gt; &gt; 
&gt; &gt; (here&#39;s a pic of an F-22 Raptor. Would house a VERY
&gt; &gt; cool-looking transformer. Top view:
&gt; &gt; http://www.f-22raptor.com/images/photos/gal_34_b.jpg 
&gt; &gt; 
&gt; &gt; Bottom View:
&gt; &gt; http://www.f-22raptor.com/images/photos/gal_38_b.jpg)
&gt; &gt; 
&gt; &gt; 
&gt; &gt; Razor smiled. &quot;There you are.&quot;
&gt; &gt; 
&gt; &gt; It resembled the classic Western showdown.
&gt; &gt; 
&gt; &gt; Razor and Strafe raised their weapons at the same
&gt; &gt; time, both firing and scrambling at the same time.
&gt; &gt; Strafe rolled on the ground and came up shooting...
&gt; &gt; 
&gt; &gt; So did Razor. 
&gt; &gt; 
&gt; &gt; Strafe retreated to the crashed shuttle, which was
&gt; &gt; experiencing a reactor leak. 
&gt; &gt; 
&gt; &gt; Razor got an idea. He fired a continuous barrage into
&gt; &gt; the exposed and damaged reactor of the Decepticon
&gt; &gt; shuttle...
&gt; &gt; 
&gt; &gt; Ka-boom!
&gt; &gt; 
&gt; &gt; Nothing but blinding light and smoke.
&gt; &gt; 
&gt; &gt; Razor laughed.
&gt; &gt; 
&gt; &gt; &quot;Dodge that, traitor.&quot;
&gt; &gt; 
&gt; &gt; The smoke took awhile to clear, and Razor turned
&gt; &gt; towards his shuttle...
&gt; &gt; 
&gt; &gt; ...To look down a double barrelled blaster
&gt; &gt; cannon....belonging to the Decepticon named Strafe, of
&gt; &gt; course.
&gt; &gt; 
&gt; &gt; &quot;Dodge this.&quot; Strafe said, the voice reverbing like a
&gt; &gt; younger version of Megatron&#39;s.
&gt; &gt; 
&gt; &gt; BLAM!
&gt; &gt; 
&gt; &gt; Razor&#39;s head had been literally blown off. The
&gt; &gt; decapitated Razor fell lifeless to the ground. The
&gt; &gt; other Decepticon who had killed him, Strafe, activated
&gt; &gt; an internal distress beacon, collapsing to the ground
&gt; &gt; in Stasis Lock, using his last ounce of strength.
&gt; &gt; 
&gt; &gt; Someone would find him, and whether it be Autobot or
&gt; &gt; Decepticon, he&#39;d either be saved or executed...
&gt; &gt; 
&gt; &gt; Of course, when whoever found him saw the logos on his
&gt; &gt; shoulders, he would probably be killed on the spot,
&gt; &gt; lest his rescuer be a trigger-happy Autobot or Maximal
&gt; &gt; wanting to bag himself a Decepticon. His last thought
&gt; &gt; before going into stasis lock?
&gt; &gt; 
&gt; &gt; The Decepticons wanted him dead, the Autobots hated
&gt; &gt; him...he was screwed either way.
